items.headline: What's the Big Idea?
items.desc:
Big Idea Wikia is a fresh,clean, and great way to know about all of their past and current shows from the company, including VeggieTales and 3-2-1 Penguins!

You can learn about the many episodes, songs, segments, the people involved with the shows, and even your characters!

You can also help out if you're a fan to these shows
